    <content><![CDATA[<p>因为想着迟早有一天要有自己的服务器然后部署动态网页，所以Hexo Next只能是过度，个人又非常喜欢Typecho这种轻量的Blog, 记录一下资源以待后续使用(给自己挖坑，悲<del>^</del>)</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<p><a href="http://101.32.194.18/4.html">http://101.32.194.18/4.html</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.typecho.wiki/themes/">https://www.typecho.wiki/themes/</a></p>
<p><a href="https://typecho.org/">https://typecho.org/</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1bJyN7LqRqQ">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1bJyN7LqRqQ</a></p>
<p><a href="https://blog.naibabiji.com/step">网页注意要点</a></p>
<p><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1005807?areaSource=106001.4">https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1005807?areaSource=106001.4</a></p>
<p><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/6969113070346403853">https://juejin.cn/post/6969113070346403853</a></p>
<p><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1900496">https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1900496</a></p>
<p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/34211709">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/34211709</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.namesilo.com/">https://www.namesilo.com/</a></p>
